title: Transformers RID 2015 S01E05 720p [TankEngine]
description:
Better late than never, here's Transformers RID 2015 S01E05 in English! This is the first place and only place I am uploading it. Please feel free to share it around but give credit where credit is due.

Chapter markings are included for your convenience.

Please note that because of the way this is broadcast, it has been upscaled to 720p and so is not "true" 720p.

Video: 

720p @ 50fps (upscaled from 576i @ 25fps)
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, H.264

Audio:

MPEG-2 Stereo @ 48kHz
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, AAC

Please enjoy this show and make sure to check back next weekend for episode 4 and beyond!

N.B.:

The opening and credits sequences were butchered by Cartoon Network (or non-existent, as was the case with the opening, where they instead repeated the first two minutes of the episode in its place). Therefore, I have sourced the Chinese versions as replacements. 
The only difference you will notice is the different watermarks (as well as the longer intro from the Chinese version - unfortunately, the version with vocals could not be timed properly with the video, but hopefully this will be fixed in the future). 
Thanks to those involved with helping me find these. You know who you are
